    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 powerplant with an 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission shifts with bolt-action precision, paired with a subframe that has been proactively reinforced to prevent common chassis fatigue. The factory finish remains deep and lustrous with no signs of oxidation, while the cabin maintains its structural integrity with zero bolster wear. A collector-grade example of the ultimate driving machine, preserved in its purest mechanical form.",
