      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that redefines the meaning of 'mint' condition. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and looks as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, free from any swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of bolster wear, the carpets are spotless under original floor mats, and every control feels crisp and tactile. Mechanically, it is flawless, accompanied by a comprehensive service history documenting every fluid change and inspection performed ahead of schedule. Every feature, from the advanced navigation system to the adaptive suspension, functions exactly as intended. This is not just a used car; it is a preserved masterpiece for the discerning enthusiast who demands the absolute best. Sold with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title.",
